---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Pavel Kleisner – Senior Backend Developer & Team Lead">

    <section class="mb-28">
        <div class="section-label mb-4">Senior Backend Developer · Team Lead</div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] gap-8 items-start">
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
                    Pavel <span class="accent-text">Kleisner</span>
                </h1>

                <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-6">
                    I build and lead backend systems that need to stay reliable for years.
                    My focus is architecture, maintainability, and clear delivery under real product constraints.
                </p>

                <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-10">
                    I combine hands-on engineering with technical leadership. Since 2023, I lead a development team,
                    mentor developers, and take responsibility for technical direction and delivery.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">View projects</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6 space-y-4">
                <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-400">At a glance</div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-700/80 bg-slate-900/60 p-4">
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">9+</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Years in software</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-700/80 bg-slate-900/60 p-4">
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">2023</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Team lead since</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-700/80 bg-slate-900/60 p-4">
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">Prague</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Czech Republic</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-700/80 bg-slate-900/60 p-4">
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">EN/CZ</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Work language</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-1">
                    <span class="pill">Java</span>
                    <span class="pill">Kotlin</span>
                    <span class="pill">Spring</span>
                    <span class="pill">Kafka</span>
                    <span class="pill">Kubernetes</span>
                    <span class="pill">PostgreSQL</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-28">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">What I bring</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Architecture ownership</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">Clear service boundaries, resilient integration flows, and systems that remain understandable over time.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Reliable delivery</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">Pragmatic decisions, realistic scope, and steady shipping cadence without hero-driven process.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Technical leadership</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">Mentoring developers, reviewing architecture decisions, and aligning engineering with product goals.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Continuous learning</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400">I actively learn by building. Right now I experiment with <span class="accent-text">Flame Engine</span>.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-28">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Experience Snapshot</h2>
        <div class="space-y-5">
            <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Senior Backend-heavy Full-stack Engineer / Team Lead</h3>
                    <span class="text-slate-400">DataLite, s.r.o.</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">January 2017 – Present · Prague</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300">
                    <li>Architecture, databases, integrations, and key technical decisions in production systems.</li>
                    <li>Long-term ownership of system stability, maintainability, and operational reliability.</li>
                    <li>Leading the development team since 2023, including mentoring and delivery responsibility.</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Sales</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">Elektro Juránek</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">August 2014 – December 2016</p>
                </article>
                <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Tester</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">GMC Software</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">November 2013 – January 2014</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-28 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Education & Certifications</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
                <li>CTU Prague, BSc - Software Technologies & Management (2009-2013)</li>
                <li>University of Pardubice - Microprocessor Technology (2008-2009)</li>
                <li>Version control system GIT, CZ.NIC (2018)</li>
                <li>Maven, Ing. Jiri Pinkas (2013)</li>
            </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="surface-card rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Community & Interests</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
                <li>Organizer, Charity in Cerveny Kostelec (since December 2015)</li>
                <li>Film screenings in Cerveny Kostelec (December 2015 - 2020)</li>
                <li>Current technical focus: experimentation and learning with Flame Engine</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-5">Interested in collaboration?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-8 max-w-3xl">
            If you need a senior backend developer or technical lead for long-term product development,
            I am open to discussing cooperation. Email is the fastest channel.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    </section>

</Layout>
